1. *Evo* tu je i moja knjiga. (Here is also my book.)
2. Našli smo *evo* sve što smo tražili. (We found here all that we were looking for.)
3. *Evo* se vidi da je neko to već napravio. (It is obvious here that someone has already done it.)
4. *Evo* se vidi da je projekat završen. (It is visible here that the project is finished.)
5. *Evo* ti moja preporuka. (Here is my recommendation for you.)